creator: DiagRight
descriptionHtml:
- You get access to incredible daily offers and weekly incentives to boost your earnings.
- Track Let’s sign-up to get started driving deliveries and making profits.

About this application
We at Diagright created the largest fleet of phlebotomists. Getting started with Diagright is rewardable and profitable for managing orders.

How to use the App ?
- Install the PHLEBO APP from Play Store and complete registration by uploading your documents
- Once documents are uploaded and submitted , we’ll verify and activate your account.
- Voila – You will start receiving orders based on the selected zone you are around
- Drive to the Pickup location , collect samples based on the details provided in the App and deliver at the Lab with real time temperature tracking.

Why this " home blood sample collection" app?
- More earnings and Profits – our low commission rates let you earn more than ever
- You can track your KMs run – thus track your earnings per KMs
- Referral Program (Refer and Earn)
- Higher the completed order, higher will be the incentives
- Opportunity to work with the Leading Laboratories and great exposure
- You will get to select your preferred working zones
- Flexibility have a vital role - no matter which city you are travelling you can continue to work with our empanelled LAB partners
- Fast Payments: You can check your daily earnings on the app, in real-time and expect to be paid every day. our performance on the app (like your acceptance rate and trip ratings) and get incentives

About Us
We are creating a logistic platform where phlebotomists could register, train and onboard themselves digitally and our model is to create an UBER like fleet. Our fleet is integrated with an IOT device which gives transparency to the end user about the sample temperature and dynamic location. This is the first time in India for a diagnostic last mile fleet. Other hand, we are going to tie up with all the bigger and smaller labs in almost 53 cities that we have planned for the first year of operation. Standardization of last mile, price comparison, report delivery TAT of 12 hour across cities are three of our major objectives.
descriptionShort: Diagnostic fleet - platform where phlebos could onboard themselves for delivery

Our fleet is integrated with an IOT device which gives transparency to the end user about the sample temperature and dynamic location. This is the first time in India for a diagnostic last mile fleet. Other hand, we are going to tie up with all the bigger and smaller labs in almost 53 cities that we have planned for the first year of operation. Standardization of last mile, price comparison, report delivery TAT of 12 hour across cities are three of our major objectives.
